<p>
  <span class="nym">Callistus</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>Κάλλιστος</i> 'most beautiful'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of three popes, one anti-pope, and a patriarch of Constantinople.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


